                Learn to Code
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Master programming with our comprehensive courses. 
                From beginner to advanced, we'll help you build real-world skills.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                <button onclick="initiateAuth('code-academy')" class="bg-white text-blue-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-lg">
                    Start Free Course
                </button>
                <button onclick="scrollToCourses()" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors text-lg">
                    Browse Courses
